snippet.title: Live Coding: Mobile App w/ NativeScript
snippet.description:
NativeScript is a way to write cross-platform native mobile applications using JavaScript. It works with JavaScript, TypeScript, Angular, and Vue! It works a lot like React Native. Let's check it out and figure out how to make a simple Android app.
